{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239670/extras/BEAST_Steam_LongDescription_Highlight_EN__1_.png?t=1734011997\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239670/extras/BEAST_Steam_LongDescription_JoinDiscord_EN__1_.png?t=1734011997\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239670/extras/BEAST_Steam_LongDescription_Title_EN_3v3Shooter.png?t=1734011997\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239670/extras/BEAST_Steam_LongDescriptionGif_3v3Shooter__1_.gif?t=1734011997\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>BEAST</strong> <strong>is a thrilling 3v3 multiplayer hero shooter</strong> where each match delivers quick and intense action with powerful Mechas! Choose your favorite character and dive into quick, action-packed games that offer easy, pick-up-and-play fun. <strong>BEAST</strong> offers a light-hearted, laid-back experience open to anyone, boasting quick matches full of excitement!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239670/extras/BEAST_Steam_LongDescription_Title_EN_Mechanimals.png?t=1734011997\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239670/extras/BEAST_Steam_LongDescriptionGif_Mechanimals_1.gif?t=1734011997\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Experience a dynamic dual gameplay system. <strong>Switch seamlessly between your powerful MECHA for brute strength and your agile PET</strong> for nimble tactics, each offering unique skills tha